, and red. Could anyone tell me (in order) the cons in DAoC??? Thanks <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulisaandbler.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lisa and Bler</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Orc Pawn</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/25/01 8:21:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Con system</span><hr size=1> Grey = way under you, no XP, no cash/items - except quest mobs, no longer agro to you<br>
Green = a lot weeker than you, XP and Cash<br>
Blue = a little weeker than you, XP and Cash<br>
Yellow - about the same level as you<br>
Orange - a little higher than you<br>
Red- higher than you, higher than orange<br>
Purple - much higher than you <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ufinndari.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Finndari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/25/01 8:23:12 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Con system</span><hr size=1> In my experience it is roughly like this:<br>
<br>
From easiest to Hardest:<br>
<br>
Grey-no challenge, too low for you. You will receive no loot or xp for these.<br>
Green-couple levels below you, easy kill.<br>
Blue-equal level or 1 level below. Should be able to kill.<br>
Yellow- a level above you, you have a chance, but more than likely will end up dead. This varies a lot on your equipment and class.<br>
Orange/Red- Good experience in a group, solo and you'll probably die.<br>
Purple- A few to MANY levels above you.  Depending on how many levels above you, even a group might have a rough time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulisaandbler.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lisa and Bler</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Orc Pawn</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/01 6:27:42 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Con system</span><hr size=1> Yellows are the same level as you, and later in levels they can be a couple levels below you as the con system has a wider range at later levels. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uamadayus65.showPublicProfile?language=EN>amadayus65</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Will O Wisp</span><br>  Posts: 121<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/01 10:56:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Con system</span><hr size=1> purple-5 lvl or more to you<br>
